quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  100,10,"Nikwisa kwilochesya papaswela yaili m’mitima?"
  100,11,"Chisimu lyele lisikulyo M’mbuje gwao (Allah) tachamanya abali syosope (syakwamba yaŵapanganyaga ŵanganyao)."
  101,7,"Basi jwalakwejo takaŵe mu ndamo jakusengwasya."
  101,8,"Nambo mundu jwachiukajepepale n'dingo wakwe (wa yambone, ni kusitopa yakusakala)."
  101,9,"Basi liuto lyakwe ni ku Hawiya."
  102,4,"Soni ngwamba! Chinchiika kumanyilila."
  102,5,"Ngwamba! Ingaŵe mwamanyililaga umanyilisi usyesyene (nga nganin'jijilikaga ni ya duniya)."
  102,6,"Chisimu chene chinkauone Moto Waukali."
  103,1,"Ngujilumbila ndaŵi."
  103,2,"Chisimu chene mundu ali nchasiko (ni kupelelwa)."
  103,3,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, ni kulimbisyanaga ya (kuya ichindu) yakuona, ni kulimbisyanaga soni yakupilila."